ated while the\nratio of the thermal energy to the gravitational energy $\\alpha$ is kept fixed.\nWe also report some basic physical data of the proto-stellar fragments that\nform the binary system, including the formation mass $M_f$, and its\ncorresponding $\\alpha_f$ and $\\beta_f$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Feb 2016 16:46:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-10"}
