proving the electronic performance\nof the 2D semiconductors, with the ultimate goal of achieving technologically\nviable atomically thin (opto)electronics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Feb 2016 18:55:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-10"}
