adio gischt relics could be modeled by adjusting\nthe shape of the fossil electron spectrum and adopting the specific\nconfiguration of the fossil cloud.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Feb 2016 06:30:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 7 May 2016 02:24:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
