e enhanced gravity by utilizing the hydrostatic\npressure assumption in the bed normal direction. Numerical calculations are\nconducted for several test cases involving steep slopes. Comparison with a\nbed-fitted model shows that even the simplified non-hydrostatic Cartesian model\ncan be used to simulate shallow granular flows over arbitrary topography.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Feb 2016 09:06:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Oct 2016 12:52:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-20"}
