izon evolution, and in addition, we investigate which\n$F(R)$ gravity can successfully realize each of the four cosmological epochs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Feb 2016 09:45:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 14 May 2016 10:04:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-01"}
